# >>> agentic-system-kit
# BEGIN AGENTIC SYSTEM KIT (v2)
#
# Goal: keep repos clean + reviewable.
# - Large, ephemeral, or machine-specific outputs live in canonical scratch zones and are ignored.
# - Small, curated docs (including run logs under docs/agent_runs/) are tracked.

# Scratch zones (allowed top-level dirs; ignore contents)
artifacts/_local/**
!artifacts/_local/README.md

reports/_runs/**
!reports/_runs/README.md

reports/_bundles/**
!reports/_bundles/README.md

.cache/**
tmp/**

# Common local environments / caches
.venv/
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*.pyo
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# Agent runner scratch (if present)
.agent/**

# Generated helper docs (rebuildable)
docs/_generated/**
docs/_bundles/**
project_state/_generated/**

# NOTE: docs/agent_runs/ is intentionally tracked (do NOT ignore).

# END AGENTIC SYSTEM KIT (v2)
# <<< agentic-system-kit
